**Usage**
`!usage` monitors the usage of system resources namely:
Gigabytes Disk Used
Disk Used
CPU Used
TCP Connections Used
UDP Connections Used
Active Memory Used
Average System Load Of The Past Minute
Mbit/s Current Bandwidth Received
Mbit/s Current Bandwidth Transmitted
Current Disk Reads Completed
Current Disk Writes Completed
Top Ten Processes By CPU Consumption
Top Ten Processes By Memory Consumption

This command is good for when the bot is slow and you want to find out why
